{"tid":222933,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"（女神變剩女）42歲林志玲爆朋友都放棄介紹對象給她了","createTime":"2017-04-30T02:38:16.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-30T12:54:06.000Z","uid":41351,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"0e075ee50484d1f8b914ca1fff1d869e8dc11f0e","tid":222933,"uid":41351,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-30T02:38:16.000Z","msg":"新歡告吹等不到桃花？林志玲自嘲「連朋友都放棄」<br />\n<br />\n〔娛樂頻道／綜合報導〕42歲的林志玲今年初被爆和大陸工程董事長殷琪的外甥「Chris」楊仁沛戀愛ing，之後又傳要閃嫁上海俞姓富豪，不過都遭林志玲否認。昨她出席活動時被問到感情狀態，笑說最近沒有新對象，更自嘲「連好友都放棄自己了」。<br />\n<br />\n據《中國時報》報導，林志玲昨替婚禮品牌老闆好友站台，看到現場各大婚禮品牌齊聚一堂，林志玲透露舉辦婚禮「有愛最重要」，希望未來能在草地上舉行戶外婚禮，並在過程中一一擁抱每位賓客，感受親朋好友的祝福。<br />\n日前林志玲的爸爸曾大讚Chris條件好，更透露小倆口的戀情「有陣子聽說有，但現在我不知道」。雖林志玲並未正面回應，但她笑說最近身邊沒人介紹新對象，更自嘲連好朋友都放棄她，未來要多靠自己一點，「就像最近的電影《喜歡&middot;你》，看到喜歡的人要勇敢告白。」<br />\n<a href=\"http://ent.ltn.com.tw/m/news/breakingnews/2051263\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fent.ltn.com.tw%2Fm%2Fnews%2Fbreakingnews%2F2051263&d=eUEb8trTAlhqW9E3j8wilwdLCpCjoNGxXEizPMjNmRM%3D&h=3a4aa67b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fent.ltn.com.tw%2Fm%2Fnews%2Fbreakingnews%2F2051263&h=0d074a80\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://ent.ltn.com.tw/m/news/breakingnews/2051263</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/04/30/103804_5eb6ad446645a1e1743f40df77a1619f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F04%2F30%2F103804_5eb6ad446645a1e1743f40df77a1619f.jpg&h=ce8bee64&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3d9a614418fd8d5faf662c769a57ce015b2aa670","tid":222933,"uid":99048,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-30T03:08:37.000Z","msg":"42歲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n下面識吸塵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cdddb2f8c393cd80b142f5e96970c020efd434a3","tid":222933,"uid":53568,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-30T03:17:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我埋單得唔得"},{"pid":"1779c282281d0cb1fc750fbae5e63ecaaaa25fe8","tid":222933,"uid":25345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-30T04:08:25.000Z","msg":"2008年出道以來，她從未談過戀愛，也很嚮往愛情。談婚姻、生育，她說：「結婚的話，任何年紀都可以，但我想要小孩子！」她最近積極轉型，透露對平凡生活的渴求，「如果我有接一些電影、電視作品，以後會跟孩子講也說不定。」她話說得豁達，但半點朱脣內終究被嗅出說不出口的無奈。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n2010年，她曾在AV作品中宣布婚訊，目前影迷分成兩派，一派認為她已是貨真價實的「人妻」，另一派認為她只是做效果。她受訪時透露：「我也常常被問這個問題！其實是那部片的設定。」她宣告單身，並笑說其實沒有很多人追求她，渴望戀愛。<br />\n<br />\n港媒日前報導她將從AV引退，但她否認，表示不是不喜歡拍AV，只是會多嘗試各種機會。<br />\n<br />\n在《沙西米》中，她的角色夏美心思細膩，常被負面情緒糾纏，她笑說，現實生活中，她個個性大剌剌。不過也常常暗自垂淚，「中學時，我奶奶去世，我因為距離無法回去看她，每次想到這件事我都會哭！」去年祖父過世，她在百忙中擠出時間送祖父一程，她才覺得解開心中的結。"},{"pid":"8951801f92b3c4141774bb654503ce8c274a121d","tid":222933,"uid":4180,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-30T04:52:56.000Z","msg":"歲你..........."},{"pid":"a3c511a49bd8be5e20a8de341fa271590e53105d","tid":222933,"uid":51828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-30T09:33:31.000Z","msg":"搵鬼佬算啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  亞洲男人自卑唔會搵你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"18b53a46a2290777d3b0ec067f6112c02bb3609c","tid":222933,"uid":55519,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-30T10:21:19.000Z","msg":"佢都唔恨拍拖啦 要揀點會冇呀"},{"pid":"e79c60c7f616461e83661557631d13d6c32a94cd","tid":222933,"uid":66203,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-30T11:19:52.000Z","msg":"42碎老女人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"588d9e0caa5bf28701cc154dd10aa4710c3dda05","tid":222933,"uid":3369,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-30T11:24:03.000Z","msg":"呢d女眼角太高，呢世都好難有人埋單<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"588840d8a3c8cf41d615baf8ad143c3510a1dfca","tid":222933,"uid":64564,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-30T11:34:49.000Z","msg":"志玲姐姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"548365923a5b337ff093baa17118522d9fc5a6ba","tid":222933,"uid":56377,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-30T12:37:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ad2c7057dea7f754388c79049bc5110664e684bb","tid":222933,"uid":49004,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-30T12:51:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>呢d女眼角太高，呢世都好難有人埋單<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n言承旭 金城武 都唔要<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ecfc62aa53a252bcbab6f47e6ebdb63f3720e1b7","tid":222933,"uid":17492,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-30T12:54:06.000Z","msg":"臭雞扮上菜"}]}